class FenwickTree:
    def __init__(self, n):
        self.n = n
        self.bit = [0] * (n + 1)

    def update(self, idx, delta):
        i = idx + 1
        while i <= self.n:
            self.bit[i] += delta
            i += i & -i

    def query(self, idx):
        i = idx + 1; s = 0
        while i > 0:
            s += self.bit[i]
            i -= i & -i
        return s

    def range_sum(self, l, r):
        return self.query(r) - (self.query(l - 1) if l > 0 else 0)
```
**Big-O:** O(log n) update/query. Cok hafif, hizli.
**Alternatif:** Segment Tree O(log n) daha esnek (range update).

